  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为安全架构设计一个看板，展示不同安全机制之间的依赖关系。第一列我想放OAuth2，它是很多流程的起点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "column1",
        "Security_OAuth2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，第一列是OAuth2。那这一列下面需要放什么任务卡片？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "column1",
        "Security_OAuth2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "OAuth2下面挂两个任务：零信任架构和防火墙配置。零信任是OAuth2认证后的访问控制策略，防火墙则是网络层面的防护。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "column1",
        "task1",
        "task2",
        "Security_ZeroTrust",
        "Security_Firewall"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "明白了，第一列OAuth2下面已添加零信任和防火墙两个任务。接下来第二列是什么？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "column1",
        "task1",
        "task2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "第二列我想直接用\"防火墙\"作为列名，但要注意——这里的防火墙任务是从第一列流转过来的，同时这一列下面要挂加密任务。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "column2",
        "Security_Firewall",
        "task3",
        "Security_Encryption"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下，第二列的列名是\"防火墙\"，和第一列里的防火墙任务是同一个概念吗？还是说有区分？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "column2",
        "Security_Firewall"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是同一个概念。我的设计思路是：第一列完成防火墙配置任务后，进入第二列的防火墙验证阶段，然后衍生出加密需求。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "column2",
        "Security_Firewall",
        "task3",
        "Security_Encryption"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，第二列防火墙已建立，下面添加了加密任务。第三列呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "column2",
        "task3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "第三列用\"加密\"作为列名，下面挂一个OAuth2任务。这表示加密机制最终又要回到OAuth2的令牌加密环节，形成闭环。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "column3",
        "Security_Encryption",
        "task4",
        "Security_OAuth2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "这个闭环设计很有意思。不过我需要确认：第三列的OAuth2和第一列的OAuth2是同一个实体吗？还是说是加密后的新OAuth2实现？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "column3",
        "task4",
        "Security_OAuth2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是同一个实体，表示加密机制反哺OAuth2的安全加固。整个看板想表达的是：OAuth2→零信任/防火墙→加密→更安全的OAuth2这样一个演进循环。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "column1",
        "column2",
